That’s what you do when bombs are going off, and when Michael Cohen takes the stand, it will be bombs away.
We already have a preview of Cohen’s opening statement wherein he calls Donald J. Trump a racist, a conman, and a cheat.
Absolutely none of this will come as a surprise to anyone who has followed the news for the past two years.
The big worry here isn’t the bomb Michael Cohen will drop.
It is the one Donald Trump will drop.